%% DevArena Judge Service — complete judging workflow
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API as Submission API
    participant SS as SubmissionService
    participant DB as Postgres (Submission)
    participant Q as BullMQ (judge-submissions)
    participant W as Judge Worker
    participant JE as JudgeEngine
    participant TR as TestCase Repo
    participant EX as Execution Engine
    participant CMP as Comparator
    participant SC as ScoringService
    participant EV as Redis Pub/Sub
    participant SOCK as Socket Layer (assumed)

    User->>API: POST /submission { problemId, language, code }
    API->>SS: create(...)
    SS->>SS: validate language
    SS->>SS: rate-limit (Redis INCR)
    SS->>DB: findRecentDuplicate (dedup guard)
    SS->>TR: problemConfig (time/mem limits)
    SS->>DB: create submission (PENDING)
    SS->>EV: publish submission.created
    SS->>Q: enqueue(jobData, priority)
    SS->>DB: status = QUEUED
    API-->>User: 202 { submissionId, QUEUED }

    Q->>W: deliver job (priority order)
    W->>JE: judge(job)
    JE->>EV: publish submission.started
    JE->>DB: status = RUNNING
    JE->>TR: forProblem(problemId) → test cases
    Note over JE: public/sample first, then hidden

    loop each test case (bounded parallelism)
        JE->>EX: run(code, stdin, limits)
        EX-->>JE: { status, stdout, time, memory }
        alt engine-level failure
            JE->>JE: verdict = CE/RE/TLE/MLE/OLE
        else compare output
            JE->>CMP: compare(stdout, expected)
            CMP-->>JE: { match, presentationError }
            JE->>JE: verdict = AC / PE / WA
        end
        JE->>EV: publish submission.running (per-case, streaming)
        opt stop-on-first-failure and failed
            JE->>JE: remaining cases = SKIPPED
        end
    end

    JE->>SC: aggregate(results)
    SC-->>JE: { verdict, score, %, peak mem, max runtime }
    JE->>DB: saveVerdict (submission + results, 1 txn)
    JE->>EV: publish submission.verdict
    JE->>EV: publish submission.completed
    EV->>SOCK: fan-out events
    SOCK-->>User: live verdict + score

    alt retries exhausted
        W->>Q: route to DLQ
        W->>DB: status = INTERNAL_ERROR
        W->>EV: publish submission.failed
    end
